PERMISSION - Principal:
    - Section
        - edit              Deny
        - view              Allow
    - Student
        - create            Deny
        - delete            Deny
        - edit area         Deny
        - edit form         Deny
        - edit info         Deny
        - edit lock         Deny
        - view              Allow
    - User
        - create            Deny
        - delete            Deny
        - edit              Deny
        - view              Allow
    - Year
        - create            Deny
        - edit              Deny
        - view              Allow
PERMISSION - Administrator:
    - Section
        - edit              Allow
        - view              Allow
    - Student
        - create            Allow
        - delete            Allow
        - edit area         Allow
        - edit form         Allow
        - edit info         Allow
        - edit lock         Allow
        - view              Allow
    - User
        - create            Allow
        - delete            Allow
        - edit              Allow
        - view              Allow
    - Year
        - create            Allow
        - view              Allow
        - edit              Allow
PERMISSION - Grade Level Coordinator / Adviser:
        - create            Deny
        - delete            Deny
        - edit area         Deny
        - edit form         Allow (limited)
        - edit info         Deny
        - edit lock         Deny
        - view              Allow (limited)
